snippet.title: Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Leo | Vijay | Trisha | Part 1
snippet.description:
In this spoiler-filled interaction with Sudhir Srinivasan, #LokeshKanagaraj talks about all things #Leo, envisioning #Vijay in the LCU, and more 

This is the first part of the interaction.   #CinemaExpress 

00:10 - 01:45  - Loki and The Kerala Story
01:46 - 02:45 - How did Loki respond to the polarising responses 
02:46 - 04:40 - How did Loki accept the criticism about the flashback
04:41 - 08.40 - How Loki fixed the duration of Leo
08:41 - 09:40 - What does Loki believe is the truth of Leo?  
09:41 - 10:54  - What is Loki's favourite thing about the Leo flashback
10:55 - 12:00 - Is Loki really constrained by fans 
12:01 - 16:16 - What does it take for young directors like Loki to work with superstars
16:17 - 20:40 - How does Loki see the audience's fixation on box-office numbers
20:41 - 24:38 - Who does Loki think is the villain of Leo? 
24:39 - 25:43 - Loki opens about the Hulk Connect in Leo
25:44 - 28:56 - Is Leo a good person or a bad person? 
28:57 - 32.30 - Is Loki glorifying the bad guy in Leo? 
32:31 - 32:56 - What is Parthiban's take on a drug-free society? 
32:57 - 33.24 - Does Loki really think the twin angle worked in favour of the film? 
33:25 - 37:58 - How does Loki work with his writing room? 
37:59 - 42:05 - Does Loki feel the pressure of casting the big names
42:06 - 50:00 - The big question of Loki and LCU
Follow us on

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/XpressCinema/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/XpressCinema
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/xpresscinema/

For more film news, interviews and reviews, go to: http://www.cinemaexpress.com

Cinema Express is a wing of The New Indian Express, and gives you the latest in the world of cinema, with special emphasis on South India, and particular distaste for gossip. The New Indian Express is published by Express Publications (Madurai) Limited from 25 centres in Tamil Nadu, Karnataka, Andhra Pradesh, Kerala and Odisha.
The company also publishes the Tamil daily, Dinamani, Cinema Express (Tamil), Malayalam Varika (Malayalam), Sakhi (Kannada), and Sunday Standard from New Delhi.

snippet.title: Battle Like Champions' Champion! (Clash of Clans Season Challenges)
snippet.description:
The Champions' Champion skin joins the pantheon of Heroes as we celebrate this year's World Championship, live on Nov 24-26! Get your tickets now at https://supr.cl/clashfest2023! 


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ‚ñ∫ https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ‚ñ∫ https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ‚ñ∫ https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ‚ñ∫ https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. http://supr.cl/ThisArmy

From rage-¬≠filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.title: PART 2 Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Leo | Vijay | Trisha
snippet.description:
In this spoiler-filled interaction with Sudhir Srinivasan, #LokeshKanagaraj talks about all things #Leo, bringing #Vijay into the LCU, and more 

This is the SECOND part of the interaction

00:00 - 5:22 - Including History of Violence, what are the other inspirations in Loki's films

05:23 - 07:00 - How did Loki sketch the husband-wife equation in Leo

07:01 - 09:44 - How did the hyena come into the Loki Universe

09:45 - 12:08 - What does Loki think of how people connect the hyena metaphor and other layers of Leo 

12:09 - 14:23 - What elevated Loki's cinematic knowledge

14:24 - 17:48 - What does Loki think of the audience understanding? 

17:49 - 19:37 - What are the plans for the hyena in the LCU? 

19:38 - 20:49 - Will Loki attempt the horror genre? 

20:50 - 23.58 - How does Loki zero in on the retro songs in his films? 

23:59 - 26:16 - How does Loki create an atmosphere for usage of these songs? 

26:17 - 27:20 - What inspired Loki to make that badass Vijay intro card?

27:21 - 28:11 - Why does Loki believe second time is the charm? 

28:12 - 28:38 - Loki on finally bringing Mansoor Ali Khan into the LCU

28:39 - 29:57 - What were the steps Loki took to ensure Parthiban's body adapted to the war scars?
 
29:58 - 32:16 - How important is Anirudh to Loki's films? 

32:17 - 34:27 - What were the various contributions of Anirudh to LEO? 

34:28 - 36:14 - How does Loki work with Anbariv to get the fight choreography on point in Leo? 

36:15 - 37:35 - Does Loki think that the stunts got a bit generic in certain scenes in the second half? 

37:36 - 39:24 - What was the most satisfying response Loki got post the release of Leo? What was his biggest takeaway? 

39:25 - 41:10 - Loki opens up on the LCU Routemap
 
41:11 - 43:23 - Loki signs off by talking about his next biggie,  Thalaivar 171

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/xpresscinema/

For more film news, interviews and reviews, go to: http://www.cinemaexpress.com

This is your chance to get up close and personal with the stars and immerse yourself in the magic of 'Leo'."

snippet.title: Emiway x Savlon Swasth India ‚Äì HAATH DHONA COOL HAI #HandwashLegend ft. The Dharavi Dream Project
snippet.description:
This Iconic Hip-Hop move üëèüèº is now the HANDWASHING Move!
Now after the hack, comes the track!

The track aims to make washing hands with Handwash or Soap cool in the minds of children, keeping them healthy and safe from various illnesses.

Let‚Äôs all wash our hands and become a #HandwashLegend.
___

ITC's Savlon Swasth India Mission - one of the largest school programmes of its kind, is committed to seeding hand hygiene habits in over 85 lakh school children, through continuous awareness and engagement activities.  
___

The Dharavi Dream Project After School of Hip-Hop is a non-profit organisation based in Mumbai. Through various educational programmes, mentorships and community engagement initiatives, it supports children living in Dharavi, Mumbai which today is known for its culturally vibrant hip-hop talent.

#HandwashingForAll #SavlonSwasthIndiaMission
___

Audio Credits:
Song :- HAATH DHONA COOL HAI 
Artist / Lyrics : EmiwayBantai
Prod by : Emiway Bantai

Episode 3917: Babita Ka Mushkil Gift
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha gets worried about Babita's gift as she wishes to have a present related to the Moon. Jetha falls asleep while engrossed in his thoughts and he dreams about it. In his dream, Jetha and Babita have landed on the Moon through a rocket. Babita is extremely happy and she shows gratitude to Jetha for fulfilling her wish. Jetha's beautiful dream gets jeopardized when Sundar appears and offers him a glass of water. Watch the episode to find out what happens further!

snippet.title: Minecraft CHICKEN vs HUNTER
snippet.description:
Minecraft CHICKEN vs HUNTER... I have to take a CHICKEN to beat the ender dragon. My friend has to stop me. Should be easy right?

Follow my socials:
‚ûΩ Twitter - @dream
‚ûΩ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Snapchat - @dream

George: @GeorgeNotFound 

This video is a different Minecraft challenge concept that we have never done before! It's similar to Minecraft Manhunt, in that I have to beat the game while George tries to hunt the CHICKEN, instead of me. The chicken heals over time like a player, and has 20 hearts.

It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftChallenge

Episode 3916: The Perfect Gift
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha apologizes to Babita for the present misunderstanding. Jetha also asks Babita to assist him in selecting an acceptable gift for his client, who is Bengali like her. Babita first hesitates, wondering how she could choose a present for someone she has never met. Later, she says that, in her opinion, sweets are a great way to win any Bengali's heart. Jetha expressly asks Babits' preference, and she responds that any Moon-related present would be her favorite. Jetha runs to Taarak for assistance. What is Jetha going to do now?

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. About Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Kaa:
------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. While united in their passion for honest and ground-breaking journalism, their contrasting characters immediately put them at loggerheads. What will happen when she starts falling in love with him despite the red flags? 'Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka' stars Shivangi Joshi and Kushal Tandon in lead roles.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Baylagaam Episode 23 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 1st November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

Written By: Huma Hina Nafees
Directed By: Zahid Mehmood
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS! Manchester United 0-3 Manchester City | Haaland (2) and Foden Goals!
snippet.description:
City turned in a masterful display to beat Manchester United 3-0 with the best performance so far this season.

Erling Haaland set the Blues on the way with a first-half penalty that was scant reward for the dominance showed.

The Norwegian headed home his second just after half-time before setting up Phil Foden for a late third.

It was no more than the Treble winners deserved after what was a stunning 90 minutes against our cross-city rivals.
